<ab facs="#facs_379_r1l25">vvie daʒ Jr vnd ewr vndertanen Jren Armman den Herman
                        Hunger von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_379_r1l30"><expan>ven<ex>n</ex>bach</expan> irret vnd enget
